      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The electric force on <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>Y</mtext></math></span></span> is repulsive and the electric potential energy increases.</p>",
